---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="The story behind Good Ear and our standards for curation.">
  <article class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="about-header">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray">About</p>
        <h1>Curation is the product.</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content">
        <section class="about-intro">
          <p class="lead">
            Good Ear exists because most record shops are overwhelming,
            and most online sellers don't care what they're selling.
          </p>
          <p>
            I started this after years of digging through bins, estate sales,
            and thrift stores. The good stuff is out there—it just takes
            time and taste to find it. That's the service: I do the work
            so you get the rewards.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="standards mt-xl">
          <h2>The Standards</h2>

          <div class="standard-list mt-lg">
            <div class="standard">
              <h3>Honest Grading</h3>
              <p>
                Every record is graded conservatively using Goldmine standards.
                VG+ means VG+, not "VG+ but actually VG." What you see is what you get.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="standard">
              <h3>Cleaned & Inspected</h3>
              <p>
                Each record is cleaned before listing and inspected under good light.
                No mystery pressings, no hidden damage.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="standard">
              <h3>Curated Selection</h3>
              <p>
                Not everything makes the cut. If it's here, it's because it's
                genuinely worth owning—musically and as a physical object.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="standard">
              <h3>Fair Prices</h3>
              <p>
                Priced to move, not to sit. I check Discogs, but I'm not trying
                to squeeze every dollar. Good deals for good records.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grading mt-xl">
          <h2>Grading Guide</h2>
          <div class="grade-list mt-lg">
            <div class="grade">
              <span class="grade-label">NM</span>
              <span class="grade-name">Near Mint</span>
              <p>Nearly perfect. May have been played a few times with care.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grade">
              <span class="grade-label">VG+</span>
              <span class="grade-name">Very Good Plus</span>
              <p>Light wear, plays great. Surface noise minimal to none.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grade">
              <span class="grade-label">VG</span>
              <span class="grade-name">Very Good</span>
              <p>Visible wear, some surface noise, but no skips. Still enjoyable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grade">
              <span class="grade-label">G+</span>
              <span class="grade-name">Good Plus</span>
              <p>Well-loved. Plays through but with consistent noise. Priced accordingly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="contact mt-xl">
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          <p class="mt-md">
            Questions about a record? Want to sell your collection?
            Just want to talk music?
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@goodear.shop" class="btn btn-outline mt-md">
            Email Me
          </a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-header {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-intro p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .standard-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .standard h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .standard p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .grade-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .grade {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 140px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .grade {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xs);
    }
  }

  .grade-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .grade-name {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .grade p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .contact {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-gray-light);
  }
</style>
